Have you
by themonk » Sun 02.27.2011 11:08 am The verb is:Ohana mi ni itagootoo ga arimasu ka? ...."Have you been to the flower viewing?" This is a tense related question
Last edited by themonk on Wed 08.03.2011 7:13 am, edited 3 times in total.
